Package main.models

Interface Seating

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
StandardSeating
public interface Seating extends Serializable
Represents the seating layout of a session, displaying which seats are booked and which are not. This interface allows for different seating types to display the seating layout differently.
